review_text: Perfect if you want to sit quietly by the water. It's not crowded at all and it's pretty clean. But there are not a lot of options for the kids, only one game for the toddlers and one for the older kids, along with two outdated baby swings.
It is a great and quite place
Beautiful, quiet park by the water
Snow Removal is lacking during Winter.

(Translated by Google) Summer and autumn are good places for people to walk and relax. Riverside scenery, fishing, and entertainment are all in their own right.

(Original)
